{
  "chapter": 23,
  "chapter_summary": "本章讲述独孤策与杜伏威在崖顶对峙。杜伏威一眼识破独孤策的碧落红尘剑法，并故意以尤楚红的哮喘病激怒对方。独孤策出剑攻向杜伏威，但仅两招便被化解，内力远逊。杜伏威劝其罢手，云玉真代表巨鲲帮认输，同意让出寇仲和徐子陵。然而寇徐二人不愿被当作货物转送，趁众人不备携手跳崖。二人落地后打碎藏在身上的四个鸡血瓶制造血迹，引来野狼群掩护逃跑，成功以鸟渡术逃入密林。杜伏威赶到崖底时被狼群争食的场景迷惑，未能追上。黄昏时二人在溪边洗濯，回忆起初遇傅君婥的时光。寇仲提出前往彭城寻找东溟夫人单美仙的计划，意图利用东溟派账簿揭露宇文阀的谋反阴谋。二人比赛穿好湿衣后，踏上了前往彭城的新旅程。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_ce",
      "speaker_name": "独孤策",
      "listener": "char_du_fu_wei",
      "text": "杜总管请。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 9,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_fu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "杜伏威",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_ce",
      "text": "江湖上用剑的人多不胜数，但真懂用剑的人却屈指可数，最负盛名莫过独孤和宋姓两家大阀。\n\n宋阀现在为了应付那昏君，自顾不暇，若本人没有看错，兄台脚步隐含奇门遁法，当是来自独孤阀名列奇功绝艺榜上的‘碧落红尘’，杜某有看走眼吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 13,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_ce",
      "speaker_name": "独孤策",
      "listener": "char_du_fu_wei",
      "text": "前辈眼力高明，晚辈正是独孤策，凭家父独孤峰指点得几下招式，请前辈赐教。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 23,
      "line_end": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_fu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "杜伏威",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_ce",
      "text": "原来真是故人之后，只不知老太太的哮喘病有没有起色呢？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 27,
      "line_end": 29
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_ce",
      "speaker_name": "独孤策",
      "listener": "char_du_fu_wei",
      "text": "老奶奶身体福安，多谢杜总管关心了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 31,
      "line_end": 33
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_fu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "杜伏威",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_ce",
      "text": "看看独孤家的‘碧落红尘’有没有点甚么新意思！",
      "tone": "挑衅",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 39,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_ce",
      "speaker_name": "独孤策",
      "listener": "char_du_fu_wei",
      "text": "得罪了！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 57,
      "line_end": 57
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_fu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "杜伏威",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_ce",
      "text": "好！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 85,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_fu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "杜伏威",
      "listener": "char_du_gu_ce",
      "text": "若独孤峰亲来，或有与我一拚之力，但世侄你却差远了。\n\n尚有八招，世侄若还要逞强出手，杜某保证你会一命不保，世侄三思才好。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 99,
      "line_end": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "云玉真",
      "listener": "char_du_fu_wei",
      "text": "晚辈领教了，杜总管可把两人带走，玉真仅代表巨鲲帮发言，以后再不插手到这件事情去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 109,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_fu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "杜伏威",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "孩子！\n\n回家了！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 113,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "士可杀不可辱，我们扬州双龙岂是可被当作货物般转来让去的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 119,
      "line_end": 121
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_du_fu_wei",
      "text": "爹！请恕孩儿们不孝了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yun_yu_zhen",
      "speaker_name": "云玉真",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不要！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 125,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_fu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "杜伏威",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不要！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 125,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_fu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "杜伏威",
      "listener": "char_yun_yu_zhen",
      "text": "你们都要陪他们死了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_fu_wei",
      "speaker_name": "杜伏威",
      "listener": "char_yun_yu_zhen",
      "text": "算了！你们快给我滚！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 149,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "这究是甚么地方呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我们沿淮水西行，后来调了头，在北岸离船，现在该是在彭城和东海两郡之间。\n\n哈！你记否得云婆娘说过那东溟夫人单美仙这几天会到彭城见李阀阀主李渊吗？\n\n若想娶东溟的美人儿小公主，我们就该到彭城去。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "你还未受够吗？\n\n现在人人都认为我们死了，不如先去老翟处找素姐，看看李大哥的情况不是更好吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "你这小子真没有志气，我们不是要报娘的仇吗？\n\n眼下明刀明枪去找宇文化骨，只会笑大他的臭口，但山人自有害死宇文化骨的妙法。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 187,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "甚么妙法？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 193,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "自然是那账簿，说不定宇文阀也有向东溟派订购兵器，好阴谋作反，否则就不会指示海沙帮去攻打飘香号了，不是摆明是要消灭自己造反的证吗？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "来！我们作个比赛。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "比甚么呢？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "比赛谁先穿好湿衣，然后再比谁的轻功好一点，可早一步踏足到彭城去。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 23,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 207
    }
  ],
